@startuml
actor User

' Application is the main system here
box "Application" #LightBlue
  participant App as "App"
  participant Func1 as "F1: collect_fin_data"
  participant Func2 as "F2: collect_emp_details"
end box

== User Request ==
User -> App : Request:\n"Distribute 50% of\nprofits based on ratings"

== Internal Data Collection ==
App -> Func1 : collect_financial_data()
Func1 --> App : Return financial data

App -> Func2 : collect_employee_details()
Func2 --> App : Return employee data

== Processing ==
App -> App : Compute bonus\ndistribution

== Final Response ==
App --> User : Final response:\nBonus breakdown\nper employee
@enduml
